warn: 24.02.2024 20:32:59.617 RelationalEventId.BoolWithDefaultWarning[20601] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Model.Validation)

info: 26.02.2024 23:20:41.637 RelationalEventId.CommandExecuted[20101] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command) 
      Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__user_Id_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT [u].[OperationClaimId] AS [Id], [t].[Name]
      FROM [UserOperationClaims] AS [u]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[Name]
          FROM [OperationClaims] AS [o]
          WHERE [o].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [o].[DeletedDate] IS NULL

      FROM (
          SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CommentCount], [a].[Content], [a].[CreatedBy], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[Date], [a].[DeletedDate], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[ModifiedBy], [a].[ModifiedDate], [a].[SeoAuthor], [a].[SeoDescription], [a].[Status], [a].[Title], [a].[UserId], [a].[ViewCount]

      ) AS [t]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[AuthenticatorType], [u].[CreatedBy], [u].[CreatedDate], [u].[CultureType], [u].[DeletedDate], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[IsDeleted], [u].[LastName], [u].[ModifiedBy], [u].[ModifiedDate], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[Status]

      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[DeletedDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsPopular], [c].[ModifiedBy], [c].[ModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status], [c].[UploadedFileId]

          SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CommentCount], [a].[Content], [a].[CreatedBy], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[Date], [a].[DeletedDate], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[ModifiedBy], [a].[ModifiedDate], [a].[SeoAuthor], [a].[SeoDescription], [a].[Status], [a].[Title], [a].[UserId], [a].[ViewCount]
          FROM [Articles] AS [a]
          WHERE [a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [a].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
          ORDER BY [a].[Date] DESC
          OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
      ) AS [t]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[AuthenticatorType], [u].[CreatedBy], [u].[CreatedDate], [u].[CultureType], [u].[DeletedDate], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[IsDeleted], [u].[LastName], [u].[ModifiedBy], [u].[ModifiedDate], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[Status]
          FROM [Users] AS [u]
          WHERE [u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [u].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[Id]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[DeletedDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsPopular], [c].[ModifiedBy], [c].[ModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status], [c].[UploadedFileId]
          FROM [Categories] AS [c]
          WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[DeletedDate] IS NULL

          SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ArticleId], [t3].[CreatedBy], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[DeletedDate], [t3].[IsDeleted], [t3].[ModifiedBy], [t3].[ModifiedDate], [t3].[Name], [t3].[Status]
          FROM [Tags] AS [t3]
          WHERE [t3].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [t3].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
      ) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ArticleId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[ArticleId], [a0].[CreatedBy], [a0].[CreatedDate], [a0].[DeletedDate], [a0].[IsDeleted], [a0].[ModifiedBy], [a0].[ModifiedDate], [a0].[NewPath], [a0].[OldPath], [a0].[Status], [a0].[UploadedFileId]
          FROM [ArticleUploadedFiles] AS [a0]
          WHERE [a0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [a0].[DeletedDate] IS NULL
      ) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[ArticleId]
      ORDER BY [t].[Date] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]
